### 🧪 Caching HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# =========================================================================
# 1. IN-MEMORY CACHE TEST (IMemoryCache)
# =========================================================================

# 1.1. Ambil data pertama kali (Akan lambat ~1 detik - Cache Miss)
GET {{host}}/api/caching/memory

###

# 1.2. Ambil data kedua kali (Sangat cepat ~1-5ms - Cache Hit)
GET {{host}}/api/caching/memory

###

# 1.3. Invalidate Memory Cache
DELETE {{host}}/api/caching/memory/invalidate

###

# =========================================================================
# 2. DISTRIBUTED CACHE TEST (IDistributedCache)
# =========================================================================

# 2.1. Ambil data distributed pertama kali (Cache Miss)
GET {{host}}/api/caching/distributed

###

# 2.2. Ambil data distributed kedua kali (Cache Hit)
GET {{host}}/api/caching/distributed

###

# 2.3. Invalidate Distributed Cache
DELETE {{host}}/api/caching/distributed/invalidate
